import { createApp } from 'vue'
import App from './App.vue'
import router from './router'
import vuetify from './plugins/vuetify'
import { loadFonts } from './plugins/webfontloader'

loadFonts()

createApp(App)
  .use(router)
  .use(vuetify)
  .mount('#app')

import './assets/assets/vendor/jquery/jquery.min.js'
import '@/assets/assets/vendor/bootstrap/js/bootstrap.min.js'
import '@/assets/assets/js/isotope.min.js'
import '@/assets/assets/js/owl-carousel.js'
import '@/assets/assets/js/counter.js'
import '@/assets/assets/js/custom.js'
